<p>THE DETERMINATION OF DAMAGE AND DAMAGE INDICES FOR REINFORCED CONCRETE BEAMS DESIGNED TO 1972 MINISTRY OF WORKS DESIGN CODES</p>
 
<div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">By</p>
